          "target": "当 Obsidian 加载插件时启动本地健康存根。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Reviewed edits mode is active. Shell commands and deletes are blocked. Approved agent-edit proposals can be applied to vault Markdown files.",
          "target": "已审阅编辑模式处于活动状态。Shell 命令和删除操作被阻止。已批准的代理编辑提案可以应用到保险库 Markdown 文件。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Optional absolute folder paths, one per line. The vault root is allowed automatically for read-only context.",
          "target": "可选的绝对文件夹路径，每行一个。保险库根目录自动允许用于只读上下文。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Vault folder for Sidekick agent profiles and memory files. Agent files live under Sidekick/Agents by default.",
          "target": "用于 Sidekick 代理配置文件和记忆文件的保险库文件夹。代理文件默认位于 Sidekick/Agents 下。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Create starter .agent.md profiles and memory files, then refresh the generated project index.",
          "target": "创建启动器 .agent.md 配置文件和记忆文件，然后刷新生成的项目索引。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Persistent Pi session name. Changing it starts using a different stored conversation.",
          "target": "持久化 Pi 会话名称。更改它将开始使用不同的存储对话。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Command or absolute path used by Pi. Non-default paths are confirmed per Obsidian session because vault plugin data can be untrusted.",
          "target": "Pi 使用的命令或绝对路径。非默认路径会在每个 Obsidian 会话中确认，因为保险库插件数据可能不受信任。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Disabled keeps Pi fully tool-free. Read-only enables Pi's read, grep, find, and ls tools from the vault root; bash, edit, and write stay disabled.",
          "target": "禁用将使 Pi 完全无工具。只读启用 Pi 从保险库根目录读取、grep、查找和 ls 的工具；bash、编辑和写入保持禁用。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Maximum time to wait for a Pi response. Larger local models and read-only tools may need several minutes.",
