        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Default sidebar status panel height. You can also drag the divider between Status and Agent.",
          "target": "默认侧边栏状态面板高度。您也可以拖动状态和代理之间的分隔线。"
