        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Exact commands the plugin may run with @cmd(...). Commands run without a shell from the vault root. Keep this short; npm scripts are intentionally not included by default.",
          "target": "插件可以使用 @cmd(...) 运行的确切命令。命令在保险库根目录下无 shell 运行。请保持简短；npm 脚本默认不包含在内。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Allow @url(...) prompt context. Requires HTTPS and an explicit host allowlist; DNS results resolving to private/local/metadata IP ranges are blocked.",
          "target": "允许 @url(...) 提示上下文。需要 HTTPS 和明确的主机允许列表；解析为私有/本地/元数据 IP 范围的 DNS 结果将被阻止。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
